1
00:00:00,075 --> 00:00:02,761
♪ (gutangiza muzika) ♪

2
00:00:29,763 --> 00:00:32,214
Muraka neza mu cyumweru cya kabiri,
kandi mwakoze kugaruka.

3
00:00:32,214 --> 00:00:33,729
Mur'icyi cyumweru tuzavuga

4
00:00:33,729 --> 00:00:36,362
mu by'ukuri urwego rumwe mu zo hambere
mu nzira yo kwihangir'umurimo

5
00:00:36,362 --> 00:00:39,024
arirwo kumeny'amahirwe
kandi tugiye kuvuga ku bijyanye

6
00:00:39,024 --> 00:00:40,489
n'uburyo wameny'amahirwe meza,

7
00:00:40,489 --> 00:00:43,113
tugiye kuvuga ibijyanye
amahirwe ushobora kutabona.

8
00:00:43,113 --> 00:00:45,992
Tugerageza gusobanukirwa ibituyobora
mu kumenya amahirwe,

9
00:00:45,992 --> 00:00:48,808
kandi tugiye kubagir'inama

10
00:00:48,808 --> 00:00:51,281
z'inzira mu by'ukuri zo
gusesengur'amahirwe

11
00:00:51,281 --> 00:00:55,044
bityo ushobora gusobanukirw'amahirwe
aguhereza ahantu heza kurush'ahandi.

12
00:00:55,044 --> 00:00:57,056
Bityo nutekereza ku
nzira yo gutangiza umurimo

13
00:00:57,056 --> 00:00:59,486
Kur'iyo ntera, ni kuruhare rwawe
n'amahirwe

14
00:00:59,486 --> 00:01:01,621
bityo niba utekereza ibijyanye
n'amahirwe amwe

15
00:01:02,245 --> 00:01:06,545
n'ugushaka amahirwe
aguha ahantu heza

16
00:01:06,545 --> 00:01:09,205
ho gutangiza umurimo,
ariko ugomba no kwibuka

17
00:01:09,205 --> 00:01:11,620
ko ubwoko bw'amahirwe
urimo gukoresha

18
00:01:11,620 --> 00:01:15,708
nibwo buzahitamo ubwoko bwo muzamenyekana
bwo umurimo wawe uzibwira.


19
00:01:15,708 --> 00:01:18,839
N'ukumenyekana k'umuryango,
kumenyekana k'umurimo,

20
00:01:18,839 --> 00:01:20,768
uwo uri we nk'umuryango.

21
00:01:20,768 --> 00:01:25,263
Nanone, uwo uri we nka rwiyemezamirimo
n'ikipe yawe ishobora kugena

22
00:01:25,263 --> 00:01:28,154
ubwoko bw'amahirwe
bwo ubona, kandi ukurikirana.

23
00:01:28,154 --> 00:01:32,922
Bityo, nabyo n'ibyingenzi gutekereza kuri
rwiyemezamirimo we ubwe

24
00:01:32,922 --> 00:01:36,110
kandi n'ubwenge bwe ubwo ari bwo
n'uburambe bwuwo muntu,

25
00:01:36,110 --> 00:01:38,030
n'uburambe bw'ikipe yose.

26
00:01:38,030 --> 00:01:40,535
Bityo, kino cyumweru tugiye
gubatangiza ku icyigwa

27
00:01:40,535 --> 00:01:42,973
cyo <i> guhinduranya kw'ikoranabuhanga, </i>

28
00:01:42,973 --> 00:01:46,297
muri make bishatse kuvuga ko
ikoranabuhanga rishobora gukoreshwa

29
00:01:46,297 --> 00:01:47,699
ku masoko atandukanye.

30
00:01:47,699 --> 00:01:49,217
Mu yandi magambo, ibi bisobanuye

31
00:01:49,217 --> 00:01:51,451
ko ushobora kuba ufite
amahirwe ya masoko atandukanye

32
00:01:51,451 --> 00:01:52,801
yo ushobora gukora.

33
00:01:52,801 --> 00:01:54,908
Ibyo biraguha
amahitamo watekerejeho

34
00:01:54,908 --> 00:01:56,871
ku cyiciro cya mbere cyo gutangiz'umurimo.

35
00:01:56,871 --> 00:01:59,681
Kand'ibyo bivuze
ko ushobora gufata amahirwe meza

36
00:01:59,681 --> 00:02:01,913
hanyuma wenda ukaba wajya no mu yandi.

37
00:02:01,913 --> 00:02:05,470
Tuzabatwara mur'
iri somo hanyuma byimbitse.

38
00:02:05,470 --> 00:02:08,236
Bityo ibyo bizamur'ikibazo
n'ubuhe bwoko bw'amahirwe

39
00:02:08,236 --> 00:02:09,853
ushobora mu by'ukuri kubona.

40
00:02:10,033 --> 00:02:11,472
Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye

41
00:02:11,472 --> 00:02:17,298
ko ba rwiyemezamirimo benshi batareba
ku miterere yuzuye y'amahirwe;

42
00:02:17,298 --> 00:02:21,641
ahubwo, bita cyane
ku mahirwe asa

43
00:02:21,641 --> 00:02:24,058
kandi ntibite kuri menshi
ashoboka.

44
00:02:24,058 --> 00:02:26,529
Mur'uwo mwanya, kand'ibi bizamura ikibazo
cya n'ukuber'iki bakor'ibi,

45
00:02:26,529 --> 00:02:28,642
hanyuma tugiye
kwiga icyo kibazo.

46
00:02:28,642 --> 00:02:31,233
Murabizi, ubwenge bw'ibanze
n'umuyobozi ukomeye.

47
00:02:31,233 --> 00:02:33,319
Ikintu kimwe kizamukir'aha ubwo rero,

48
00:02:33,319 --> 00:02:36,133
n'ukuntu mu by'ukuri ureba cyane
imiterere yiryo hirwe

49
00:02:36,133 --> 00:02:39,244
rishobora no kuguha
amwe mu mahitamo wetekerejeho,

50
00:02:39,244 --> 00:02:41,925
n'amahirwe amwe yo guhitamo
amahirwe yawe.

51
00:02:42,569 --> 00:02:46,509
Bityo ucyimara kubona amahirwe atandukanye
ikibazo kamere kirazamuka--

52
00:02:46,509 --> 00:02:48,590
n'irihe hirwe mur'aya
riyaruta?

53
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,176
Bityo twatanz'agace kamwe

54
00:02:50,176 --> 00:02:52,855
ku kibazo cya ni ayahe
mahirwe meza

55
00:02:52,855 --> 00:02:54,470
bishoboka kuba ufite mu biganza byawe,

56
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:56,855
bityo tugiye kugutwara
mu nzego 7 zoroshye

57
00:02:56,855 --> 00:02:59,300
z'uburyo wa suzuma ukana gerageza
amahirwe atandukanye

58
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:02,241
hanyuma ugashaka ni ayahe
meza yo gutangiriram'umurimo.

59
00:03:02,241 --> 00:03:06,026
BItyo urabona, twibanze ku bya ngombwa
byo mu nzira yo gushak'amahirwe

60
00:03:06,026 --> 00:03:08,911
amahirwe ubona,
ubwoko bw'amahirwe utabona,

61
00:03:08,911 --> 00:03:11,562
-uburyo uyasesenguramo,--
-n'uburyo uyagenzuramo.

62
00:03:11,562 --> 00:03:14,451
Hanyuma bityo, ibi bizagufasha
mu rwego rwa mbere

63
00:03:14,451 --> 00:03:17,692
rwo mur'urugendo rwawe nka rwiyemezamirimo,
bityo gumana natwe.
